works.description: The Royal wedding fever has gripped the whole world, and the celebrations are in full swing. While Lancashire-based Colin Bleasdale planned to mark the Royal Wedding Day by making an expensive ice cream, famous luxury department store Harrods in London is celebrating the big wedding with an exquisite collection of tiered designer wedding cakes. These meter-high wedding cakes will be showcased in the store’s Brompton Road windows from April 26 until April 30, 2011.
